               <msContents>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i1">
                     <rubric>Nomina sacra; name of the donor; name of the scribe; names of the king and metropolitan; incipit of Text I; incipits of the prayers to be read; directives to the ministers and their abbreviations; elements of the punctuation signs; elements of Ethiopic numerals. &#xD;
On the incipit page of Text I (fol. 1r) and in fol. 25v, a few lines are rubricated (alternating with black lines).</rubric>
                     <incipit>
                        <foreign xml:lang="en"/>
                     </incipit>
                     <explicit>
                        <foreign xml:lang="en"/>
                     </explicit>
                     <note/>
                  </msItem>
                  <msItem xml:id="coloph1">
                     <colophon>
                        <locus target="35v"/>Fol. 35v: ተፈጸመ፡ ጸሎተ፡ ዕጣን፡ አመ፡ ፲ [fol. 36r] ወ፩፡ ለወርኃ፡ አብ፡ በዕብራውያን። በዕለተ፡ ሠሉስ፡ በ፲ወ፭ሰዓት፡ እንዘ፡ ወንጌላዊ፡ ሉቃስ፡ በ፸ወ፱ዓመተ፡ ቀ፡ ን፡ በ፲፻ወ፰፻፸ወ፱ዓመተ፡ ምሕረት፡ ወጸሐፊሁ፡ ቀሲስ፡ ኃይለ፡ ኢየሱስ፡ ዘውእቱ፡ ርእሰ፡ ደብር። ወሰብሐት፡ ለእግዚአብሔር፡ ከሃሊ፡ ወፈጻሚ። ላዕለ፡ ኵሉ፡ ግብር፡ ዘበሰማይ፡ ወዘበምድር። አሜን። ኪርያላይሶን።<foreign xml:lang="en"/>
                        <note>The colophon mentions the date 1879 A.M. (=1886-87 A.D.) and the name of the scribe, priest Ḫaylä ʾIyäsus, the priest and the head of the church (rǝʾǝsä däbr).</note>
                     </colophon>
                  </msItem>
